race.comment: FERNCO NEL NZ (9) has won five of his last six starts, including last start over 1660m at Albion Park, scoring by 10 metres when sent out as the $1.15 favourite. Having his first start here and can make it a winning one. DOUBLE LOU (8) is looking for black-type success after scoring as the hot favourite when leading all of the way over 1609m at this track last time out. Looks hard to beat again. FINAL DEADLINE NZ (10) was an impressive winner all of way winner last start over 2138m at Albion Park, getting home by 12 metres to score a hat-trick. Ready to run another big race. SWEET ON LEXY (2) comes here following a third in a Group One event over 1609m at this track, beaten 6 metres. Ideally drawn and has top-three claims in a fresh-up state.
